Task 7:-

Setup a remote repository in Local , Add a file and commit or save the changes and push to master branch

Steps:-
1. Created a Identity using the following commands:-
    git config --global user.name "Mayank"
    git config --global user.email "jangidanshu184@gmail.com"

2. Created a new local directory for the project using the command following commands:-
     mkdir myproject
     cd myproject

3. Initiallized a git repository using the command **git init**

4. Created a new file using the command **echo "# myfile.txt** or ** touch myfile.txt**.

5. Added all the changes to the staging area using the command **git add .**

6. Commited the changes using the command **git commit -m "Initial commit".
